  "url": "https://www.ada.lk/breaking_news/\u0dbb\u0da2\u0dba\u0dd9\u0dad\u0dca-\u0db4\u0dde\u0daf\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0d9a-\u0d85\u0d82\u0dc1\u0dba\u0dd9\u0dad\u0dca-\u0db4\u0dc4\u0dc3\u0dd4\u0d9a\u0db8\u0dca--\u0dc3\u0db8\u0dcf\u0db1--\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dd2\u0dba-\u0dba\u0dd4\u0dd4\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dba\u0dd2/11-396625",
  "time_ut": 1661498995,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0dbb\u0da2\u0dba\u0dd9\u0dad\u0dca \u0db4\u0dde\u0daf\u0dca\u0d9c\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0d9a \u0d85\u0d82\u0dc1\u0dba\u0dd9\u0dad\u0dca \u0db4\u0dc4\u0dc3\u0dd4\u0d9a\u0db8\u0dca  \u0dc3\u0db8\u0dcf\u0db1  \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dd2\u0dba \u0dba\u0dd4\u0dd4\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Facilities should be equal in government and private sector",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The United National Party Chairman, P.M., said that the government machinery of Sri Lanka should be used for the good of the nation, and that the President Ranil Wickremesinghe has already implemented the method for that. Mr. Vajira Abeywardena stated.",
        "He said that the facilities available to those in the government mechanism as well as in the private mechanism should be the same and if such facilities are provided, many people will not try to enter the government mechanism in the future.",
        "Mr. Vajira Abeywardena said this while speaking to the media in Colombo today (26). He further commented there and said:",
        "\"There are 60 to 70 lakhs in the private sector and 17 to 18 lakhs in the government machinery. Both these parties are necessary for the good of Sri Lanka. Many people who go through the government mechanism go and run the private mechanism at a different speed.",
        "Not really the government mechanism, if the number of employees in a private organization is too high, that employee should find another place. In some cases, experienced groups in the government machinery require a different security approach. There is a need for a system in which the same rights are given to the government mechanism and the private mechanism.",
        "President Ranil Wickremesinghe has thought. He has presented certain matters in principle that are compatible with it. Most of the people come to the government mechanism on two things. Consistency until one dies. The other thing is that some people think that working and not working are the same.",
        "Therefore, the state machinery should be used for the good of the nation. For that, all Sri Lankan citizens have been required to have a safe system up to the deathbed. I see that the President has a plan for that, if we go there, no one will try to enter the government machinery in the future. So until you get there, I have to say that you should not do politics with this doubt. Do not connect this to politics. It has to be said that it is better to think about this for the good of the nation.",
        "The state machinery needs some transformation. Even if he leaves here, he will become a servant somewhere else. If he wants to be an employee somewhere else, a change in the economy will be necessary. If he is leaving here for a place to live, it does not matter whether he is in the government machinery or in the private machinery. Meanwhile, we have many circulars issued throughout history. He can go and serve in the countries of the world and he can create security when he comes back. In the meantime, you can go willingly and be given the opportunity to enter the private sector. So there are decisions to be taken for the good of the nation. We should take it without fear.\""
      ],
